import React from 'react'; import MagicGrid from 'magic-grid'; import MG from 'react-magic-grid'; function MGtest() { let magicGrid = new MagicGrid({ container: '.container', animate: true, gutter: 30, static: true, useMin: true }); const masonrys = document.getElementsByTagName("img"); for (let i = 0; i < masonrys.length; i++){ masonrys[i].addEventListener('load', function(){ magicGrid.positionItems(); }, false); } return (
); } export default MGtest;
